  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Site Supervisor",
  "description": "<h3>Job Description:</h3><ul><li><p>Supervise and coordinate daily interior fit-out works at site</p></li><li><p>Ensure works are carried out according to drawings, specifications, and schedule</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with subcontractors, workers, and suppliers</p></li><li><p>Monitor work quality and ensure compliance with safety regulations</p></li><li><p>Attend site meetings and report work progress to Project Manager</p></li><li><p>Resolve site issues and coordinate rectification works</p></li><li><p>Ensure proper housekeeping and site discipline</p></li><li><p>Assist in material checking and site measurements</p></li><li><p>Prepare simple site reports and updates when required</p></li></ul><h3>Requirements:</h3><ul><li><p>Relevant experience in <strong>interior design / renovation / construction works</strong></p></li><li><p>Able to supervise workers and subcontractors independently</p></li><li><p>Basic knowledge of construction drawings</p></li><li><p>Able to communicate in English (spoken)</p></li><li><p>Willing to work on site and overtime if required</p></li></ul>",
